Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Williamsburg summit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x04x
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 May 1983
International monetary conference plan comes after French endorsement of arms policy at Williamsburg summit.The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less